snippet.title: GRID 2 Reloaded Edition for Mac trailer
snippet.description:
GRID 2 Reloaded Edition is speeding towards the Mac!

Get behind the wheel of a top notch car and race your way from the streets of Paris to California's coastal highway and on to Abu Dhabi's unique Yas Marina circuit as the star driver of the up-and-coming 'World Series Racing' league.

For news, updates and information, follow us on Twitter...
